#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:22
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Using the man ioslave you are able to read the man pages installed on "
#| "your system. It is easy to use:"
msgid ""
"Using the man KIO worker you are able to read the man pages installed on "
"your system. It is easy to use:"
msgstr ""
"Ved brug af man-ioslaven kan du læse man-siderne der er installerede på dit "
"system. Den er nem at bruge:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the sections of the manual, click to find the rest."
msgstr "Se afsnittene i manualen, klik for at finde resten."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<command>man:</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable>"
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the man page of <command>fopen</command>."
msgstr "Se man-siden for <command>fopen</command>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<command>man:</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable>"
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the man page of <command>fopen</command> in section 3."
msgstr "Se man-siden for <command>fopen</command> i afsnit 3."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:50
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<command>man:</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the index of section 3."
msgstr "Se på indeks for sektion 3."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:57
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<command>man:</command>intro<replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgid "<command>man:/</command>intro<replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:</command>intro<replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the introduction of section 3."
msgstr "Kig i indledningen til sektion 3."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are more than one man page of the name that you have entered, you "
"will get a list where you can choose the man page that you want to see."
msgstr ""
"Hvis der er mere end en manualside med navnet du skrev ind, får du en liste "
"hvor du kan vælge manualsiden du vil kigge på."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a shortcut: <userinput><command>#fopen</command></userinput>, "
"which has the same effect as above."
msgstr ""
"Der er også en genvej: <userinput><command>#fopen</command></userinput>, som "
"har samme virkning som ovenfor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not find all your man pages, adjust the configuration file "
"<filename>/etc/manpath.config</filename> (or a file of a similar name "
"depending on your distribution) or adjust the environment variables "
"<envar>MANPATH</envar> and <envar>MANSECT</envar>."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke finder alle dine manualsider, så justér indstillingsfilen "
"<filename>/etc/manpath.config</filename> (eller en fil med lignende navn "
"afhængig af din distribution) eller justér miljøvariablerne <envar>MANPATH</"
"envar> og <envar>MANSECT</envar>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As with any other &kde; ioslave, it is possible to enter a &URL;, like "
#| "<userinput><command>man:socket</command></userinput> in <emphasis>any</"
#| "emphasis> &kde; application. Try it in &kwrite; and you will see the man "
#| "page in &HTML; format."
msgid ""
"As with any other KIO worker, it is possible to enter a &URL;, like "
"<userinput><command>man:/socket</command></userinput> in <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> &kde; application. Try it in &kwrite; and you will see the man "
"page in &HTML; format."
msgstr ""
"Som med andre &kde;-ioslaver, er det muligt at indtaste en &URL;, såsom "
"<userinput><command>man:socket</command></userinput> i et "
"<emphasis>vilkårlig</emphasis> &kde;-program. Prøv det i &kwrite; og du vil "
"få man-siden at se i &HTML;-format."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contact mailing list: <email>kde-devel@kde.org</email>"
msgstr "Kontakt postlisten: <email>kde-devel@kde.org</email>"

